reviews.content: It won’t work if you don’t have the stock weather app downloaded, and you also can’t have the stock weather app follow you for weather. You have to lock it to one city/town.

iPSE 13.5 Unc0ver - works
iP6S 12.4 Unc0ver - crashes the OS (doesn’t work)
Works for me running iOS 13.5 on a iPhone SE 2020.
